Package de.oth.blocklib.world.vegetation

Class Rule

java.lang.Object
de.oth.blocklib.world.vegetation.Rule
public class Rule
extends java.lang.Object
This class serves as the production rule for the L-system. A Symbol exist with its corresponding production result. This can be one or multiple results.
Author:
Julian Sellner
